xkcd-substitutions
------------------

Substitutions that make reading the news more fun!

Fetch random articles from https://www.reddit.com/r/news,
substitute them xkcd style.

Inspired from https://xkcd.com/{1288,1625,1679}/.

Setup
    [+] sudo pip install -U newspaper requests
    [+] git clone https://github.com/clickyotomy/xkcd-substitutions


Usage
    read.py [-h] [-w N] [-d http [text ...]]

    Substitutions that make reading the news more fun!
    https://github.com/clickyotomy/xkcd-substitutions

    optional arguments:
      -h, --help            show this help message and exit
      -w N, --width N       text width; default: 80
      -d http [text ...], --debug http [text ...]
                            enable debugging


Note: `substitutions.json` will be updated when a new issue of the comic is
      released.
